</p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0in" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1"><b><u><span style=
=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif">Putting fo=
rward new legislative proposals to strengthen our tools to fight corruption=
 and money laundering</span></u></b><b><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;font=
-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif">:</span></b><span style=3D"font-siz=
e:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif">&nbsp;
 The Administration is releasing draft legislation that would:&nbsp; <b><u>=
