<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:.5in"><b><u><span style=3D"font=
-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif"><o:p><span style=
=3D"text-decoration:none">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></u></b></p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0in" type=3D"disc">
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0in" type=3D"circle">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1"><span style=3D"fo=
nt-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif">Increase transpa=
rency into the &#8220;beneficial ownership&#8221; of companies formed in th=
e United States by requiring that companies know and report
 their true owners;<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
</ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:1.0in"><span style=3D"font-size=
